## text

### Source (en)

~~~text
It is important to think early about ownership and permissions. Who will have the authority to decide later about the use of the reference data? Will a single person or single organisation be responsible for this?

Please note as well that many kinds of data can not be "owned"; you can only have copyrights on specific data collections, and those data base rights are not as universal as creative rights on other works.
~~~

### Translation (zh_Hant)

~~~text
及早思考所有權與權限問題是很重要的。日後誰將有權決定這些參考資料的使用方式？此事是否將由單一個人或單一組織負責？

另請注意，許多類型的資料其實無法被「擁有」；您只能對特定的資料彙編享有著作權，而這類資料庫權利也不像其他作品上的創作權利那樣具有普遍適用性。
~~~
